Add this code to your file:
  import sys
  import os
  sys.path.insert(0, os.path.abspath(os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__name__), '../..')))
Note: It should be placed before the importation

After that
1. Place the test folder outside api folder
2. Open a docker terminal of the project container
3. Inside type: 
                ls
                cd tests
                cd utils
                python -m unittest nameofthefile.py
